    "More advanced techniques such as word embeddings and pre-trained language models were only used after 2017 to represent clinical notes for subsequent NLP tasks.",
    "Similarly, the number of studies that used rule-based approaches declined after 2014, with more advanced approaches such as machine and deep learning methods emerging.",
    "Summary of resultsThis review underscores the nascent stage of employing NLP on unstructured data in hypertension research is still at its nascent stage, with a smaller number of studies and less use of advanced NLP methods, compared to in other fields such as cancer and Intensive Care Units.",
